## File Structure

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [index.html](file:///c:/Users/vivek/.vscode/portfolio/index.html) | Full page markup with semantic HTML5 |
| [index.css](file:///c:/Users/vivek/.vscode/portfolio/index.css) | Complete design system — tokens, themes, components, responsive |
| [main.js](file:///c:/Users/vivek/.vscode/portfolio/main.js) | Theme toggle, scroll animations, mobile menu, contact form |
| `assets/` | Avatar image and hero background |

## Sections Built

| # | Section | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | **Hero** | Bold name with gradient accent, tagline, CTA buttons, social icons, scroll indicator |
| 2 | **About** | Two-column layout with avatar, professional bio, highlight badges |
| 3 | **Skills** | 4 categorized cards (Frontend, Backend, Database, Tools & DevOps) with hover effects |
| 4 | **Projects** | Featured StockFloww card + 2 project cards with tech tags and links |
| 5 | **Experience** | Timeline layout with 4 milestones — freelance, internship, hackathon, certifications |
| 6 | **Contact** | Two-column: social links + clean contact form with visual submit feedback |

## Features Implemented

- ✅ **Dark / Light mode** — Smooth toggle with localStorage persistence
- ✅ **Scroll reveal animations** — Elements fade in as they enter viewport
- ✅ **Active nav highlighting** — Auto-highlights current section in navbar
- ✅ **Mobile responsive** — Full hamburger menu + responsive grid layouts
- ✅ **Mouse glow effect** — Subtle radial gradient follows cursor
- ✅ **Micro-interactions** — Hover lifts, border glows, button transforms
- ✅ **Contact form** — Submit with loading → success visual feedback
- ✅ **Resume download** — CTA button links to `assets/Vivek_Dalimbkar_Resume.pdf`
- ✅ **SEO optimized** — Title, meta description, Open Graph tags, semantic HTML

## Design Aesthetic

- **Typography**: Inter (headings & body) + JetBrains Mono (code/tags)
- **Color palette**: Deep navy dark mode with electric indigo/purple accents
- **Style**: Vercel/Linear-inspired — clean borders, glassmorphic nav, balanced whitespace

> [!TIP]
> To make the **Download Resume** button work, place your resume PDF at `assets/Vivek_Dalimbkar_Resume.pdf`.

> [!NOTE]
> To deploy, just upload the folder to **Vercel**, **Netlify**, or **GitHub Pages** — no build step needed. It's pure HTML/CSS/JS.
